{"text": "No pay-to-win microtransactions, day one DLC, loot boxes or any other of the tropes that plague modern shooters.  Just a solid blend of fast paced realistic combat with a Vietnam setting that offers Battlefield-lite game modes with helicopters and automatic rifles.  There is currently only a handful of maps, but devs have said more are being worked on along with support for community maps.  The game scales very well thanks to UE3.  Have had a lot of fun and have only experienced improvements since closed beta.  For a small indie team, RS2: Vietnam really shines.  Highly recommended if you like team based shooters!", "appid": "418460", "steamid": "profiles/76561197969385634", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496232000.0}
