{"text": "Well have only played a couple hours so far but seems like this is going to be a great game. The fun part that im loving about this game is that is an original city builder and it also has rpg elements mixed in. As you build your city and start to progress, mythical monsters will try to attack your city and villagers.A top priority must be placed on gathering food, as well as other supplies. then there are several options for you to utilize in defense of your city. You can surround with walls and towers to shoot down attacking creatures, and continue to watch it grow. i am loving the originality of this game, and i can definitely see myself enjoying this game for hundreds of hours. As the game progresses (developer is very active and responds to all comments and concerns in a very considerate manner) and more content is added, I can only imagine what a monster this game will become. So far, greatly enjoyable, and i have only touched the tip of the iceberg. This gsme is a must have for all city builder/rpg fans. I have always loved city builders, and this one is in a class of its own. I can not wait to see what more comes to this game!", "appid": "328080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198242546108", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1469620800.0}
