{"text": "Give it a few hours to get going. This game is really addictive. Cops can be a pain, but once you learn the locations to escape them, it's not so bad. Money isn't difficult to acquire and cars aren't that expensive. Customisation options are fantastic and the range of cars is fine. Story is OK (maybe a little cliche) but still actually enjoyable. Having a great time so far.", "appid": "1222680", "steamid": "profiles/76561198229708612", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592654400.0}
