{"text": "I enjoy playing Combat Force a lot. I've always been an FPS gamer and I'm very passionate over my favourite games like CS:GO and the Battlefield and Call of Duty series. However, I didn't particularly enjoy the Zombie game mode of COD for several reasons. Combat force completely revokes the aspects why I loathed COD Zombies.  As soon as you start the game, you feel how passionate Matt Sowards and HaDe Games have been working on their newest release. It's a huge step up from their former releases, while still offering their game at a very low price point. As of now, Combat Force focuses on being a zombie survival shooter with several aspects of progression, but the developer plans to implement a multiplayer mode along with a story mode in 2020, which I am looking forward to. I highly recommend buying this game if you enjoy first-person shooters and survival games, but even if you do not, Combat Force might change your mind. It's an excellent game and truly is a jewel of its genre. You can't go wrong by spending a couple of bucks on this.", "appid": "1172430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060509161", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575633600.0}
