{"text": "Mythgard truly is an amazing card game! Here's why: This card game will at least be in my favourite 'Top 5' card games of all time \"hands down\".. It's not perfect in regards of cheating or hacking (which is a known problem online), however this game oozes quality and potential rarely seen in any other card game out there! There are a few things you need to consider as a novice, and those mainly involve grinding through the single player content (which has been offered for free and is quite lenghty) or potentially investing a lot of time and money into the game if you're looking to be really competitive at some point or another..  Surely one might be able to acquire most if not all by playing if you're really good (especially through championships and whatnot) for real money and gem - crystal rewards etc. that allows you to earn what you \"previously\" could not.. That being said, this game is actually quite newbie friendly, if you stick to the single player aspect well before looking to compete online.. So please keep this in mind and you'll surely enjoy the game for countless hours to come. The devs have just added their first expansion (with great success) to their game and it's wonderful to see how this is opening up so many new & exciting ways to play with, making it feel as if it's a totally fresh experience altogether even after houndreds of invested hours (and some money) and counting.. I can only wish for a continued support from the devs and fans, and hopefully the matter of cheating - hacking will be resolved shortly (that should always be a priority imho). Therefore i highly recommend Mythgard with a personal score of 8.5/10 (potentially 9.5/10 in due time)", "appid": "839910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198029242857", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600516800.0}
