{"text": "I think half life is one of the best games I played, even if it‚Äôs sound like a clich√©, this review will show you. The story is about a doctor called Gordon freeman, that went one day to black mesa, the place where he works, to help finishing the new project of that company, tha will make everybody remember them, as the best science company, over aperture science. But the project somehow broke, and open a gate, to aliens, some of them are the head crabs, and it‚Äôs up to you, to survive. Without any spoilers, the story of this game is great, the weapons feels very fun to use, and the bosses are strong, but once you learn how to kill them, you wouldn‚Äôt see them again for a long time. The game is very fun, and know where it‚Äôs the time to let the player some quite, where to surprise you, and when you think it‚Äôs over, it‚Äôs not. The game, even if it is FPS, still uses s lot of game puzzles, that let‚Äôs you use your brain, game puzzles that don‚Äôt effect the gameplay or making the game less boring, and can make it more of an action game, like you need to solve the puzzle, while fighting against enemies. While the game Is very fun by the term of single player, unlike the other games you used to in this years, the multiplayer felt for me less fun, and the game lacks for today standards in term of graphics. First, the multiplayer of the game, feels less balanced with strange but strong weapons, like a mosquitoes weapon that locked on the enemy, a lot of RPGs (because of quick) and many more. The graphics of this game aren‚Äôt what you want to play at 2018, because the game made in 1998, and the graphics then aren‚Äôt a masterpiece. But over-all, if you still didn‚Äôt play this game, I think you should play if you like FPS games, because you will see you wouldn‚Äôt disappointed. Game‚Äôs pros and cons: Pros: -\tFun gameplay -\tFully game story  -\tGreat story -\tFun puzzles -\tKnows how to surprise the player when he don‚Äôt expect it. -\tRemembered main character. Cons: -\tBad graphics (at least for 2018). -\tBad multiplayer.  -\tNothing else more then the multiplayer and singleplayer. Game settings: -\tFPS. -\tPuzzle game. -\tRequire potato to bad computer conditions to run. -\tParts single player (auto save sometime). -\tRequire some skills to play. -\tViolent game. -\tScience fiction game. I give this game 9/10", "appid": "70", "steamid": "profiles/76561198166364533", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1524916800.0}
