{"text": "Takes exactly one hour to finish, if you are not in a hurry. Got all the achievements and did not even get to the last few missions. I am impressed that the trucks even slide in this game. The second truck is slightly faster. There are no people in the city and the only challenge is to find the appropriate colour car. It was somewhat a pleasant and cheap compilation of roads, buildings, trucks, Dacia cars, and grass. But not that great and I see a lot of more effort could have been put into this. 10/10 would tow Dacias again - that's kind of accurate. And yet it lacks so much that I can't give it a thumbs up. P.S.: If this was 49 cents, people could have given it a thumbs up. It's just short and lacking.", "appid": "876870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198101035178", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1568289600.0}
{"text": "This game is probably appealing to many, but it reminded me way too much of what high school romance is like (Even though they are supposed to be in college). This game left me rolling my eyes, recognising all the dramatic subtext that I probably used myself at that age. This game also left me feeling dirty    I don't know, maybe teens will get more appreciation from this game. Maybe even some adults.  This is just one of the most disatisfying waste of time games I've played to date. On the plus side, I got all of the achievements in 40 minutes.", "appid": "417860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065289104", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1450526400.0}
{"text": "Eh, pretty boring. Not a great take on the Match-3 (in this case Match-4) genre. You basically make enough matches to gain resources to build dungeon rooms, which just entails clicking on a desired room, then populating them with minions. It is not as fun as it sounds. Part of the problem is that it is not particularly fast paced on the matching -- it is super slow and dull. And it's a little vague and hectic when placing your minions. The balance is off. I still prefer games like Hunie Pop and Puzzle Quest over this.", "appid": "340360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052935907", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1536667200.0}
