{"text": "Verdict: Not recommended even if you get it for free. I got it for 1‚Ç¨ and I still feel robbed. + Steam trading cards (4 drop out of 8) Steam achievements OST is not bad but it is nothing to write home about - The controls are incredibly clunky You are forced to fight waves of the same enemies over and over  One of the ugliest games I have ever seen The game often zooms on models ... and those are damn terrible I got literally stuck on the first level 3 times because the initial portal to tutorial wasn't there Abbandoned with no updates fixing bugs The combat is really booring It missses everything that made Overlords 1 and 2 fun floating enemies, unkillable enemies, enemies going into terrain ... It isn't fun ... do a few steps, do arena fight, do a few steps, another arena fight ... repeat until you finish the level", "appid": "306670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004625267", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602331200.0}
